title: Plat support looking for team for clash / ranked and other tournaments
body:
Heya! 

I'm a support main, super chill - so I don't like people who are ragers.

Just looking for people to play some games with as a team, whether it's clash, ranked flex, or we look into playing in some amateur tournaments. I don't know many other people my rank to play with!

Add Zeyzal in game (I know haha, I'll probably change it soon anyway)
